Package: idlescreen-cosmic
Version: 2.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: IdleScreen <jerydleuck@gmail.com>
Depends: idlescreen, idlescreen-applet, idlescreen-savers
Recommends: idlescreen-tui, idlescreen-cli
Provides: trance-stack
Description: IdleScreen full stack for COSMIC Desktop
 Metapackage that installs the IdleScreen daemon (idlescreen), the COSMIC
 panel applet (idlescreen-applet), and all official savers
 (idlescreen-savers). Recommends the optional TUI controller.
